{"tid":247537,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴終擴大95折優惠範圍 明起現金客都有份","createTime":"2017-05-18T00:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T17:48:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c3638e25629ae62de9cce2a3f06e36f05bfc78","tid":247537,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/085723_679a917175abcd2d4a0dbc34895afac7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F085723_679a917175abcd2d4a0dbc34895afac7.jpg&h=78832bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴5月起一連兩個月推出車費95折優惠，但只適用於八達通付款，以現金付車資者仍要支付原有車費，惟巴士上的車資顯示屏卻只顯示優惠價，造成混亂，亦令「現金客」感不滿及不公平。九巴表示，由5月19日（星期五）起，九五折車資折扣優惠計劃將擴大受惠範圍，乘客以現金或八達通乘搭九巴全港約400條獨營路線（K12、K14、K17及K18路線除外），都可受惠，優惠期直至2017年6月30日。<br />\n<br />\n計劃不適用於已享有半價優惠之十二歲以下小童及六十五歲或以上之長者，或使用「政府長者及合資格殘疾人士公共交通票價優惠計劃」的乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56707444&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56707444%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170518&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=225cc129\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56707444%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170518&h=8d7e198c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56707444&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170518</a>"},{"pid":"4bf13b04778f25081e6c87c7b50ccc2e0efaa7c2","tid":247537,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf3e1da13b12221670ee63098fda7bc3a82b987a","tid":247537,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}